If I drop a file from my desktop onto a Confluence web page, it uploads that file as an attachment.

This can be a helpful feature, but I frequently drag web shortcuts from my desktop to a browser with the intent of navigating to that page.  I never intended to upload the LNK file as an attachment to the confluence page, causing undesired edits, triggering undesired notifications, etc.

There should be a way to disable this feature on a per-page, or per-space basis, as it is useful to some, but disliked by many others at our installation.
